{
  "texts": [
    "It encompasses six main data types: webpages, scholarly papers, code, books, social media, and encyclopedia.",
    "For each data type, specific design principles and processing details are openly disclosed.",
    "This corpus has been instrumental in training the OLMo model.",
    "Notably, its creators have transparently disclosed the selection of data sources and provided a detailed overview of the data curation process.",
    "• MNBVC (MOP-LIWU Community and MNBVC Team, 2023)."
  ]
}